<REFEX REG08-TYPE="pronoun" EMPHATIC="no" HEAD="rel-pron" CASE="genitive">whose</REFEX>
</ALT-REFEX>
</REF>
 Magnum opus, Midnight's Children, was in 1993 declared the "Booker of Bookers". 
